gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 128, Lakers 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Lakers, 128-110. Stephen Curry led the Warriors with 32 points, six 3PT, and eight assists as Andrew Wiggins (20 points) and Trayce Jackson-Davis (17 points, five rebounds) totaled 37 points. Anthony Davis led the Lakers with 27 points and 15 rebounds in the loss.
